Widak-nni i d-ițeffɣen seg wezgen, llan di tejmaɛt n Ludikus azeggaɣt, qqiment waṭas n iberdan iwakken ad tebɛen abrid i d-yemmeslayen s tegrawliwin yellan di tmurt-agi.
D Sidna Ɛisa i gețṛuḥun mkul yiwen seg-sen ɣer wanda yebɣa ad iṛuḥ, ɣas akken bɣan ad steɛfun fell-asen. Aṭas seg wid i gumnen s Sidna Ɛisa yețzid irennu. Atah wayen yedṛan yid-sen, isselmad-iten deg umkan-nsen.
Ad iɛaqeb widak-nni i gxeddmen ccɣel-agi i ɣ-d-ițțunefken, i kunwi daɣen d imezwura i Sidi Ṛebbi a ten-id-tețțunefkent s tugeț !
Amakar iwɛeṛ i wid yellan dinna, ama di leḥjab-nni neɣ di lexla. Walit acḥal i geɣli tikli-nwen deg ubrid n Sidi Ṛebbi !
D lbaṭel zerɛen ara d-megren, țțafen lfeṛḥ-nsen mi xeddmen ɛinani lebɣi n tnefsit-nsen.
?ef wayen yeɛnan ajmaɛ n yedrimen i cudden-t ɣer yixef n wuzzal, iwakken ad yenɛețțaben aț-țewtem ; ma d igellil amek ara nefṛeq i wiyaḍ.
Leɛqiṛa-nni tḥețțem ɣef yemdanen, meẓẓi neɣ meqqeṛ, d igellil neɣ d ameṛkanti, d akli neɣ d aḥeṛṛi, ad wwten ticṛaḍ deg ufus ayeffus neɣ deg unyir-nsen,
wid yețmeslayen ad xeddmen ayagi s lebɣi n tnefsit-nsen, ur xeddmet ara lxilaf ger lemfaṣel, ur nessin lhiba, ur ggaren ara di lecɣal n wexxam-nsen, ur țḍuṛṛun ara iman-nsen d aweḥḥi-nsen, imi wiyaḍ xeddmen ayagi s lebɣi-nsen.
M'ara d-taseḍ, awi-d yid-ek abeṛnus-nni i ǧǧin deg ubeḥnuq, abeɛda wid yețnuzun iman-nsen, d ayen ur nețțamen ara.
Mkul yiwen deg-sen iwwet iɛeddan di tegzirt-nni ; ddant yid-es igellil iwakken ad iɛeddi rrif n tegzirt-nni ;
Di tlemmast n yiḍ, yiwet n taɣect tɛeggeḍ-ed : Atah mbla ma yeḍlem-ed yiḍ !
Tejreḥ tasa-w ɣef wannect-agi meṛṛa. Deg ussan-nni, m'ara bɣun ad xedmeɣ yiwen, aț-țṛuḥim di targit, aț-țṛuḥeḍ aț-țeččeḍ aț-țețțusellkem di tudrin n tmurt-agi ;
Ițmeslay-asen-d akka iwakken ad yedṛu wayen i d-nnan si tejmaɛt n watmaten yellan di tmurt n Yahuda yellan di lexṣaṣ, neɣ m'ulac ad kellxen i wid i gellan di tejmaɛt n watmaten.
Di yal tamdint i deg ɛeddan, țxebbiṛen atmaten s lewṣayat yellan di tebṛaț i d-fkan Sidi Ṛebbi, nehhun-ten ad tebɛen lewṣayat-agi.
Deg ussan-nni, llan wid yesɛan azal akteṛ n wiyaḍ, ma d wid ara yilin fell-asen ad rnun yid-es. Meɛna ur ilaq ara ad yedṛu wayen yuran di tira iqedsen : Adɣaɣ-nni izemren ad fehmen ayen i d-yeqqimen seg-s.
axxam n lǧameɛ, yețqiṛeb-ed snitrat ɣef tjajdit yellan di mkul amkan. Zzin-as-d daɣen amkan anda țxelliṣen tabzert !
Aṭas n lɣaci ssan iceṭṭiḍen-nsen deg ubrid, m'ara bɣin ad walin ayen yețwaṛekḍen, m'ara slen i ṣṣut n warrac yerna a d-yeččaṛen s wul yeččuṛen d zzux.
M'ara ț-zzin azeggaɣ am temagrin, zzzzin-as d lkețțan azeggaɣ ɣlayen, ț-țilawin ț-țilawin yumnen s Sidna Ɛisa yețzad irennu.
Aṭas n leǧnun țemfaṛaqen wway gar-asen, daymi ur zmiren ara ad ṛuḥen ɣer mkul amkan iwakken a d-aɣent lǧețța s wayes ara tfeǧǧeǧ deg waṭas n wussan.
Aṭas seg wid iwumi i d-yenna Sidi Ṛebbi : Semman i d-ițeffɣen seg yimi-s, wid yețwaḥeqṛen ; llan daɣen kra n yemdanen i d-yețwaceggɛen-ț-id ɣuṛ-es, llan daɣen seg waṭas n lɛaddat i d-yusan si mkul tama.
Atah wayen ara sen-d-smektiḍ : deg yiwet n temdint ur bɣin ara ad ṭṭfen imukan imezwura di mkul amkan anda țxelliṣen tabzert ( leɣṛama ), wid akk yellan di tmurt-agi, ur țṛuḥun ara alamma ț-țaɛebbiḥent iman-nsen.
Di tazwara, llan gar-aneɣ ur nezmir ara a nzux seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit. Deg webrid-agi yexlan, ț-țezmert n lewqam, aṭas n yemdanen i d-innulen seg weqṛaḥ n temdint ɣer tmurt n Truwas.
Ur țsetḥin ur țneḥcamen, xeddmen anagar leɛṛuṛ yerna ur sɛin ara leqniɛa.
Dɣa aṭas n lɣaci i gellan, yerna aṭas daɣen i d-yusan si zzman-agi ; yețmeslayen seg wat Isṛail, i gebnan ayen yedṛan yid-sen, axaṭer aṭas n lɣaci i gumnen s Sidna Ɛisa.
Llan deg-s lewqat agi n tejmaɛt i gxulfen liman-nneɣ di lecɣal n Sidi Ṛebbi ideṛṛun di zzman-agi ! Aṭas i gxeddmen lecɣal-agi mbla ma ț-țaɛkumt, ayen ara sḥasab yid-sen.
S tideț m'ara ɣ-țṛebbin yețɣiḍ aɣ lḥal imi akken i t-id-usan, s wakka ara d-uɣalen ɣer webrid n Lmasiḥ.
M'ara ț-țerren ɣer wakal tețțuɣal d ulac, meɛna m'ara d-teḥyu, a d-teḥyu s ccan d ameqqran. M'ara ț-țerren ɣer wakal teffeɣ-iț tezmert, m'ara d-teḥyu a d-teḥyu s lǧehd d ameqqran.
Di tmurt nأستراليا, aṭas seg wid yellan dinna i d-yusan ad ɛeggden di temdint n Luṭ. Imeslayen-agi iwakken ur bɣin ara a d-uɣalen ɣer webrid n Sidi Ṛebbi.
