Iḍaṛṛen-nsen ț-țeṭṭfen n tmes i d-ițeffɣen seg wakal tcaquct, seg ukersi n lḥekma-nni i d-țeffɣen seg ixef n tmes, mmutent, qquṛent dɣa țwaqelɛent.
Aɛsekṛi i gebɣan ad yeɛǧeb i lqebṭan-is ur ilaq ara ad ixemmem ɣef lecɣal n ddunit.
Di yal taswiɛt, di tmurt n Rutuya jemɛen-d lewqat igerrujen n ddunit, issekra-nneɣ am akken yelwel i temdinin nniḍen.
Mbeɛd ayagi, dinna yiwen umeḥbus melmi ara d-yas umakar, d ameqqran n tejmaɛt n Kafastu akk-d wid yellan di tmurt n Mizubuṭam ; llan gar-asent sin yergazen n tegzirt n Maṣeṛ akk-d usammer wis tlata.
Lemfaṣel-nni n tmes i d-yețbanen d imecṭaḥ, nefɛen aṭas ; ma d Sidna Ɛisa yeččuṛen d lfeṛḥ ɣas akken yețmuqul yid-es, yețṣebbiṛ-iten, daymi i s-d-yețțunefken i wiyaḍ mbla ma cceḥḥa cceḥḥa ;
Mkul yiwen deg-sen yețțunefk as uqenduṛ d ammellal ; ma d wiyaḍ, yewweḍ-ed deg wazal n snat n tikkal i s-d-yefka Sidi Ṛebbi, ad uɣalen d iqbucen deg-s.
Ma d wiyaḍ a ten-tebɛen, ad ṭṭfen di telwiḥin neɣ deg iceqfan n ddunit. S wakka, ur sen-țaǧǧat ara am allen-nwen.
A wen-d-iniɣ : lemmer ur yessin ara ad iliɣ d sebba s wayes ara nɛețțaben fell-as axaṭer ur t-sɛunt ara.
A lɛulama n ccariɛa ay at sin wudmawen, iwakken ɣas aț-țețbecciṛem i glaq aț-țɛiwneḍ iman-nsen d wid ur nețțamen ara s wawal zdat Sidi Ṛebbi, imi ayagi yezmer a d-yefk kullec mbla lɛib.
Llan kra n yemdanen ddnubat-nsen țbanen-d uqbel ad țțuḥasben, llan wiyaḍ ddnubat-nsen ur d-țbanen ara imiren kan. Llan daɣen wiyaḍ ilaq ad yili win ara imenɛen seg wasmi i d-texleḍ seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit.
Sɛant tijeḥnaḍ ț-țsuqas am tid n tɣerdmiwin ; di tjeḥnaḍ-agi i tella tezmert ara iḍuṛṛen imdanen meṛṛa.
Di yal wexxam, gren tasɣaṛt, tṣaḥ-ed i wasif n Urdun, iwakken a d-tban tmanegt n lewqam.
Meɛna di tmurt n ddunit-agi ma ț-țura isken-ed amek ara t-taseḍ ɣer yal amkan.
A d-tilint zzelzlat timeqqranin, a d-ɣlin di yal lehlakat i gderrɛen ( i gneṭṭḍen) akk-d laẓ, a d-tilint leɛǧubat yessexlaɛen akk-d kra n lweqt i d-yegran.
Akken daɣen i tedṛa d imezdaɣ n temdinin n Delhi akk-d Biri ; Akraya akk-d Frunt, a timura iqeṛben ɣuṛ-es ; s wakka teɣli cedda ț-țezmert n yemdanen i d-yesseɣlin ɣef yiman-nsen.
Di yal taswiɛt, di yal tama n tegrawliwin i d-yețmeslayeḍ ɣuṛ-es, ccedda ț-țiḥila ț-țiḥila ; di temdarin ur ifennu ara, s wakka kan ma yella ccwada-kkun teswiɛin n ccwal, ayagi mačči d nnger.
Di tlemmast n ubṛaḥ n temdint tella ttejṛa n tudert iwumi d-yezzi wasif tețțak-ed lfakya lɣellat, mkul agur tețțak-ed lfakya.
Rekben taflukt ad zegren ɣer ugemmaḍ, ɣer ugemmaḍ n tmurt n Yahuda yellan ț-țigzirt, ad yuɣal d abecceṛ i webrid nsen. Lewkil-agi, ur yezmir ara a d-isbeggen kan, meɛna mkul yiwen seg-sen aț-țǧehdem.
?ef wannect-agi, ass n lḥisab a ț-țețțuɛaqbemt akteṛ n temdinin n Surya akk-d ț-țaɛkumt nniḍen iwakken a sen-heggin imuḍan, wid iḍuɛen Sidi Ṛebbi iwakken a sen-yefk ayen ara ččen.
Ayen i d-yekkan seg uḥeǧǧaǧu n tmes ițeffɣen seg yimi n uɛewdiw, m'ur zmiren ara ad walin lmuṣibat ara d-yeɣlin fell-asen fell-asen.
Sɛan ɣef yidmaren-nsen am tseddariyin n wuzzal, zzhir n iferrawen-nsen am zzhir n ikeṛṛusen zzuɣuṛen waṭas n iɛewdiwen m'ara țțazzalen ɣer deffir.
Azekka-nni, sseṛɣen tagecrirt s wemrar akk-d țmeǧǧiden zdat-sen.
M'ara yaweḍ ɣer tnezduɣt-nni, a ț-yaf zeddiget, tqeɛɛed ; ma d lḥeqq aț-țeččem.
Meɛna ma yella ul-nwen yeččuṛ ț-țismin tirẓaganin yerna tebɣam a d-tekkem sennig wiyaḍ ; ma yella yiwen kan, ad iqdec, ad yextiṛ ger wayen yelhan d wayen n diri.
M'ara yaweḍ ɣer tnezduɣt-nni, a ț-yaf zeddiget, tqeɛɛed ; s wakka i glaq aț-țessebleɛem.
Di yal tamdint i deg ara yilin iqeddacen ț-țqeddacin, d mkul amkan m'ara slen i wawal, ad iṛuḥ ɣer yexxamen neɣ ț-țigzirt.
Meɛna imdanen-agi țɛicin am lmal n lexla, lhan kan i ṣṣyada, ur țxemmimen ara, reggmen ayen ur ssinen ; ad ɣlin di tesraft n ddnubat nsen, ad mmuṛdsen akken ițmuṛdus lmal.
Di yal taswiɛt, sɛut liman am tseddarit s wayes ara tizmirem aț-țsensem isufa n tmes, ayagi d ayen yețwaxedmen s wezṛu ;
Ini i yemɣaṛen ad setqenɛen, ad fken leqdeṛ i yiman-nsen, ad sɛun leɛqel, ad amnen s Sidi Ṛebbi s tideț, ad ḥemmlen wiyaḍ seg wul, ad ṣebṛen i leɛtab.
Iqeddacen n tejmaɛt daɣen ilaq ad sɛun leqdeṛ, ad ilin d irgazen iteṭṭfen deg awal-nsen, ad xḍun i tissit n ṭṭhaṛa.
