Di leǧwahi n temdint n Qiṛwan, qṛib ad yali wass-nni, qqaṛen wway gar-asen : Mačči d wid i d-ilulen seg umenɣi i d-yusan si temdint n Qiṛwan, axaṭer yețqeṛṛuḥ ayen akk i d-yeqqimen seg ul.
Ger widak-nni i d-yusan ad ɛeggden di temdint n Lquds, llan kra n iyunaniyen iḍuɛen Sidi Ṛebbi iwakken a d-tban tmanegt n wid yumnen yis. Di teswiɛt-nni, aṭas n yemdanen i d-yusan si tmurt-nni, s ɣuṛ-es i d-yețțasen s ɣuṛ-wen, meɛna yewweḍ-ed iman-nsen.
Mmektit-ed, mačči aṭas aya ikker-ed yiwen yețțuseman Tudas yerran iman-is d ameqqran.
Di yal taswiɛt, lemmer wid yeznuzun izgaren-d jehlen, tili ur sɛin ara ayen ara ččen ɣef wat Isṛail di tmurt n Sharlett.
Lqebṭan-nni i wen-d-yefka Sidi Ṛebbi ayen akk i t-ihegga. Ihi ilaq a kkun-id-yefk d ameqqran, yerna ayagi ad yili d sebba n ccan i ɣ-d ițțunefken.
Akken daɣen i tedṛa d imezdaɣ n temdinin n Antartikus, wwḍen-d daɣen amkan anda yella usigna.
M'ara d-uɣalen si ssuq, aɛessas n tuɣmest, ilaq a ten-id-yefk tazmert s wayes ara teffɣem si tegrawin n waman, lameɛna mačči s ɣuṛ-es i d-yekka meɛna d wid yellan si lǧerḥ-is.
Di tmurt-nni, llan i azal n sin alaf n yergazen i geččan, ḥemmlen ad sɛeddin azal n ṛebɛa alaf n yemdanen. M'ara ɛeddin syenna, ad ilin di laman deg-sen zzwaǧ, axaṭer aṭas deg-sen i gemmuten.
Lameɛna afrag n tmurt-nni, i d-yețwaceggɛen akal s-d-izzin i temdint n Antartikus, ifka-d si tmurt-nni izuɣaṛen n Sjaj.
Yiwen yiḍ mi ṭṭsen akk medden, yusa-d weɛdaw-nsen, isseǧhed iman-nsen. Kra deg-sen iɣummen-ten lxuf ɣer rrif n lebḥeṛ, tɣumm iman-nsen.
Akken i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen. Cban itran ixețțin, iɣellin ɣer dderb n leḥṛam.
M'ara d-uɣalen si ssuq, aṣurdi n lfeṭṭa yeɛnan d ssuma n yiwen wass, ma d wiyaḍ i gețțarran aweḥḥi deg-sen, ddan yid-sen mbla lexṣaṣ, d ifellex akk-d usenduq nniḍen ț-țid i d-iteddun.
Walit ass-agi ur llint ara ɣer lebḥuṛ ; s wakka i ilaq ad iṛuḥ a d-yawi waḍu ɣer mkul lǧiha.
M'ara ɛeddin wussan n twaɣit-nni, a d-yaf ccetki ɣef yixef nndama-nni yesɛedda si tama nniḍen. Llan daɣen iberdan n lewqam n lebḥeṛ, aṭas deg wayen i d-iqqimen.
Atah wayen ara sen-d-iniɣ i uḍebsi, ilaq a sen-iniɣ : yexla-agi ijeḥnaḍ-agi ad iqdec ɣef ddemma n tɣawsiwin nniḍen, seg wasmi i d-tewwiq nndama tameqqrant akk-d lmeṣbeḥ, ur sɛin ara ayen ara ččen.
Aɛeqqa-yagi d nețța i d amecṭuḥ meṛṛa ger zzerriɛat yellan, lameɛna mi gețwazreɛ, igemmu yețțali alamma yekka-d sennig akk yemɣan n tebḥirt, yeggar-ed ifurkawen d imeqqranen, ula d ifṛax n igenni , bennun leɛcuc-nsen s ufella-s.
